<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Disposed" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Disposed,</orth> absolutely, == inclined to merriment: <cit><quote>Boyet is --d,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 2.250" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL II, 250</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to make my lady laugh when she's --d,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.466" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 466</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>he does well enough if he be --d,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 2.3.88" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 3, 88</bibl></cit>. cf. <emph>Ill-disposed.</emph>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>